Directed by Akarsh Khurana

Written by Lisha Bajaj. Kanika Dhillon. Kanika Dhillon. Aniruddha Guha. Aniruddha Guha. Akarsh Khurana. Nanda Periyasamy

Cast Taapsee Pannu(Rashmi Vira). Priyanshu Painyuli(Gagan Thakur). Abhishek Banerjee(Eeshit Mehta). Supriya Pathak(Bhanuben). Manoj Joshi(Ramnik Bhai). Chirag Vohra(Nilesh Bhai (as Chirag Vora)). Shweta Tripathi(Maya Bhasin – Doctor). Supriya Pilgaonkar(Savita Deshpande – Judge). Varun Badola(Dilip Chopra). Mantra Mugdh(Coach Mukherjee (as Mantra)). Zafar Karachiwala(Mangesh Desai – Lawyer). Aseem Hattangadi(Pravin Sood (as Aseem Jayadev Hattangady)). Kritika Bharadwaj(Vaidehi Sharma). Namita Dubey(Priyanka). Zarin Shihab(Anushri (as Zarin S)). Fami Basumatary(Fami). Shwetha Gadad(Shatabdi (as Shweta V Gadad)). Katyaani(Arpita – Lawyer (as Katyaani Pandey)). Lisha Bajaj(Nurse). Dharak Chhaya(Kartik). Dhwanish Chhaya(Paresh). Boloram Das(Coach). Apeksha Iyer(Nurse). Kshitee Jog(Doctor). Goral Joshi(Sakhi). Sarthak Kakar(Jolly Bakshi). Dilshad Khurana(Doctor).Al Hasan Milad. K M Rasheduzzaman Rafi(Theguru). Ojas Rawal(On Field Reporter). Faiyaz Shaikh(Reporter 2). Priyanka Singh(Asst Coach Garima). Chahat Tewani(Young Rashmi)

Language Hindi

Producers Neha Anand. Kalpesh Damani. Ghanteshwar T. Guru. Pashan Jal. Salona Bains Joshi. Sonia Kanwar. Pranjal Khandhdiya. Ronnie Screwvala. Amish Shah. Faiyaz Shaikh. Yogiraj Shetty. Joshua Shirsath. Sanjeev Verma. Sanaya Irani Zohrabi.

Production Mango People Media. RSVP.
